lown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:13:29.000Z","msg":"唔好話聖經唔關香港事，美國好多決定都係要問過牧師嘅意見"},{"pid":"a128bac5b1300631d1bfd2a31683c54eeb95037f","tid":1786314,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:13:59.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯好地地做乜要打以色列先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36674ccd3a77f241321724567d3b726988ccdb8c","tid":1786314,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a128bac5b1300631d1bfd2a31683c54eeb95037f","tid":1786314,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:13:59.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯好地地做乜要打以色列先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"唔知佢會用咩理由啦，總之佢地三個依家個態度就係賴死唔走，仲搞結盟，唔係想搞事就奇"},{"pid":"7f765bd6b35763d0e3de0ab1bc0fb1ebd83eb46f","tid":1786314,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"點解十王唔係歐洲現存十君主（唔計安道爾）？"},{"pid":"a125f04374252474615c34ee8f7a39b93bf0902d","tid":1786314,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd1d6e61fdb4582f3adf9d356b34fbe5d2d81d5a","tid":1786314,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T05:57:15.000Z","msg":"都就黎 2020 年，都仲咁多人反猶太"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"猶太人呢啲小圈子社會去到邊都唔會受歡迎,所以佢哋先會圍爐取暖."},{"pid":"b386faba99db6108cb644268dfff09bdc4880f45","tid":1786314,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ceb1550e117374ea88b0e821912fad843e68c32","tid":1786314,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"458a2b68e0d657ab8c33f2feec4b24c548ea2918","tid":1786314,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T05:46:53.000Z","msg":"我相信中共係十王嘅其中一王，但佢應該唔會加入攻打以色列，唔會係被拔除嘅三王之一，對大家黎講可能比較可惜，但大家未必得唔到想要嘅野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T05:52:19.000Z","msg":"但佢應該係先知書中嘅「東方王」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmo